Privacy Policy

This privacy policy governs the use of the Muslim Life Guide app and outlines how the App collects, uses, and discloses personal information. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this policy.

Information Collection and Use

The Muslim Life Guide app does not collect any personal information from its users. The App only provides access to the Quran, Adkaar, and prayer time information. We do not collect any user data, including device information, location, or usage data.

Third-Party Services

The App does not use any third-party services that collect personal information from users.

Security

The Muslim Life Guide app takes reasonable measures to protect the personal information of its users. We use secure servers to store any information we collect.

Changes to this Policy

The Muslim Life Guide app may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the date at the top of this policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at mahdiababneh37@gmail.com.
